style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">这次</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">创业大赛，食界玩家轰炸大鱿鱼将</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">现场制作台湾小吃，就是要让济南人吃上地地道道的台湾小吃，品尝台湾味儿。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">说到鱿鱼，常吃是铁板鱿鱼，轰炸大鱿鱼也就是近一年来才火起来的。食界玩家轰炸大鱿鱼，大陆最早做轰炸大鱿鱼的品牌，以全套产品技术、工艺、设备、主辅用料……等优势，悉心研磨整理、开店实践检验而创建的项目，一经推出，应者云集，反响空前，在大陆掀起一股轰炸大鱿鱼的“飓风”，追随者也如雨后春笋般的模仿校之。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">食界玩家轰炸大鱿鱼精选最大尾的深海大鱿鱼，进行整形、去皮、腌制、裹浆、上粉等多道加工工序，经高温炸制成熟后，再采用专利脱油设备进行成品脱油，既保证了轰炸鱿鱼肉质软嫩弹牙，外皮焦香酥脆，又确保入口没有普通油炸食品的油腻。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">其多种</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">外撒粉料和外刷酱料</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">更是让人叫绝，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">椒盐柠檬、椒盐芥末、蜂蜜芥末、泰风酱烧、古味蒜香、孜然、香辣、麻辣、咖喱、海苔、甘梅等</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">，每一种风味都让人垂涎欲滴，更有</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">专门配制的独特台湾风味的“古早鱿鱼酱”、“酸辣鱿鱼酱”等不同酱料</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">；</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">最大程度低满足了不同消费者的口味要求，让人吃得“鱿”滋“鱿”味</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">，回味无穷</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">食界玩家轰炸大鱿鱼</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">严把每个环节，精化各项操作。经营模式简单，低投入高回报。选址极其容易：<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">平米</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">就可开</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">店，学校，车站，路边，档口，商超</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">……只要是人群密集的地方，就可以开店；操作极其简单</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">：</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">总部</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">统一</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">将</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">鱿鱼半成品配送到店，标准工艺轰炸制作</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">天就可学会，</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">人就可开店</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">；</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">利润</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">极其</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">丰厚：半成品<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">至</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元，经过炸制后成品售价</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">12</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">~</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">18<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元，利润巨大，日销</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">条，月利数万元。投入极其微小：一次性支付加盟费</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万元，装修等开办费用</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">1</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">~</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万元，</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万元以内总投资，换来月利数万元的火爆鱿鱼店</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\">。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-size:12.0000pt;font-family:\'宋体\';\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">关注</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">2014<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">中国（山东）创业加盟展</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\">，加盟食界玩家轰炸大鱿鱼，梦想在心中点燃，创业在脚下实现！</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:宋体;\"></span></p><br>符合北京甲子餐饮管理有限公司代理商要求的客户可以直接留言与厂家联系。');
