ndent-count:1.5000;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff0000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\">抗疲劳、壮阳、补肾气首选元动力。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff0000;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">配料成份：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%;text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">黄秋葵、酵母抽提物、赤藓糖醇、益生元（低聚异麦芽糖）。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">应用功效</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%;text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\">壮阳</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\">、补肾；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%;text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\">2、</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\">抗疲劳</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">提耐力</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%;text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">3、补营养、调肠道</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%;text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\">4、</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">降血脂</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">护肝脏</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">作用机理</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:150%;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\">黄秋葵</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\">经研究发现，黄秋葵富含黄酮，具有调节内分泌等功效。但其壮阳作用与化学药物伟哥不同（伟哥主要作用于局部），它是通过全身的调节（抗疲劳、增耐力、促血液……）而逐步发挥作用，故其作用更温和而持久，无副作用；黄秋葵对剧烈运动后对血乳酸的恢复具有明显的促进作用，对血清尿素氮，也有明显的降低作用。以上有力的证明了黄秋葵具有提高耐力、减轻疲劳的功效；秋葵的粘性物质中含有可溶性纤维素、果胶、多糖等，固能有效降低血清胆固醇，预防心血管病，也起到保肝护脏的作用，相对于化药伟哥来讲，作用持久，更安全。<br />酵母抽提物主要成分为多肽、氨基酸、核苷酸、B族维生素及微量元素。其快速补充营养，迅速恢复体力。<br />低聚异麦芽糖能够吸附脂类，其代谢产物能够抑制胆固醇的合成，增殖的有益菌不但能对胆固醇的吸收起同化作用而且还能产生胆固醇还原酶，还原酶可使胆固醇转化为难以被人体胃肠道所吸收的粪甾醇，起到降血脂的作用；同时低聚异麦芽糖还具有增强抗体水平、增殖肠道有益菌、抑制有害菌、减少肠道毒素、净化肠道之功效。<br />赤藓糖醇纯生物发酵、绿色安全、是天然零热量的甜味剂。口服后不参与糖代谢和血糖变化，故宜于糖尿病患者。<br />&nbsp;<br />适用人群<br />表现为 <br />2、感觉身体乏力、困倦、疲劳感的人群（也适合更年期人群）。<br />表现为记忆力减退，注意力不集中，精力不足，工作效率降低，健忘失眠，情绪常难以自控、易怒、烦躁、焦虑、抑郁等人群。<br />3、适合具有尿频、尿急、浑身乏力的糖尿病患者<br />4、适合“三高”及其因长期服药引起脏器受损的人群。</span></p><br>符合禹城雨田生物科技有限公司代理商要求的客户可以直接留言与厂家联系。');
