ont-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:28pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">增加了</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">产品适口性</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">口感细腻</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">，其</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">细度</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">达</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">120-150<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">目</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">，彻底</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">改变了麦麸</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">的</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">粗糙感</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:28pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">3<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、破壁使细胞浆膜得到利用，细胞浆膜被称为活性多糖，是提高免疫的营养物质。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:28pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">四、特殊工艺麦香天然：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:28pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">经过特殊技术处理的小麦膳食纤维粉麦香浓郁，天然麦香使您可以感受大自然的美味，</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">不需要添加</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">任何香味剂。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:28pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">五、</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">高</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">膳食</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">纤维</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:28pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">1、</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">膳食纤维细胞破壁且含量高达<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">40%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">；</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:28pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">2、</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">吸水性强，口感细腻，麦香浓郁，活性多糖利用率高。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:28pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">3、</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">小麦膳食纤维粉中的不可溶性膳食纤维占<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">96%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，可溶性膳食纤维仅占</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">3.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left:21pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">六、高矿物质：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:28pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、矿物质含量丰富，锌、镁、钾、铁、铬</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">是</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">其他糖尿病食品的</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">5<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">倍以上。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:28pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、脱除植酸提高了麦麸中矿物质的吸收率。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:28pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">七、市场同类产品比较：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:28pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">可溶性膳食纤维<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">克</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">粪便</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">膨大率<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">1.2</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">倍</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">；不溶性膳食纤维<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">克</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">粪便</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">膨大率<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">5.2</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">倍。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:28pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">可溶性膳食纤维对肠胃的刺激性较小</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">不溶性膳食纤维刺激肠胃蠕动减少热量的吸收</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">，减肥、通便、降糖效果更佳</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:28pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">3<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">可溶性膳食纤维</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">在</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">人体内易产生酸性液体，长期食用会造成</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">结直</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">肠癌；不可溶性膳食纤维</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">不产酸，无任何副作用</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:28pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">4<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、市场可溶性膳食纤维售价偏高，是我们产品价格的两倍以上，我们的产品物美价廉。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:28pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">八、</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">国内外资料证实：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">96%<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的动物膳食纤维实验选用的是麦麸。可溶性膳食纤维用于实验的较少。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">九、</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">四川大学公共卫生学院的动物研究证实：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;text-indent:28pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">超细麦麸（</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">100--200<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">目</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">）降体重和降血脂作用明显。我们的小麦膳食纤维粉细度</span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">130-150<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">目，比起单纯粉碎效果更好，是通便秘、降血糖、减肥和降血脂的天然植物美食。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height:18pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">十、邯郸县福瑞社区卫生中心部分高血压患者试吃两个月，血压平稳下降，有效率高于<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">81%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'宋体\';font-size:14pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"></span></p><br>符合邯郸市亿隆食品有限公司代理商要求的客户可以直接留言与厂家联系。');
INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('4174','解酒护肝酵素 是由中国保健食品招商网会员发布的调节血脂类招商信息：<br><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p><p style=\"border-bottom:medium none;border-left:medium none;padding-bottom:0cm;text-indent:21pt;margin:0cm 0cm 6pt;padding-left:0cm;layout-grid-mode:both;padding-right:0cm;background:white;word-break:break-all;border-top:medium none;border-right:medium none;padding-top:0cm;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid #F1F1F1 .75pt;mso-outline-level:1;mso-layout-grid-align:auto;mso-padding-alt:0cm 0cm 8.0pt 0cm;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\">什么是酵素？它不是药，也不是营养保健品，它是人体必需的基础营养物质，是人体的生命之源！它是维持人体正常的新陈代谢和免疫能力的关键要素。南通独一酵素就是这样一家有<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>年技术沉淀的纯天然酵素领导品牌。专注古法陶翁酿造工艺，坚持做<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>让每个人都能喝得起的好酵素<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>。</span></p><p style=\"border-bottom:medium none;border-left:medium none;padding-bottom:0cm;text-indent:21pt;margin:0cm 0cm 6pt;padding-left:0cm;layout-grid-mode:both;padding-right:0cm;background:white;word-break:break-all;border-top:medium none;border-right:medium none;padding-top:0cm;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid #F1F1F1 .75pt;mso-outline-level:1;mso-layout-grid-align:auto;mso-padding-alt:0cm 0cm 8.0pt 0cm;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">马云说，<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>下一个能超过我的人，一定出现在健康产业里！<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>未来<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>年，在老龄化趋势加快、亚健康状态日益普遍的背景下，<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>大健康<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>产业将成中国经济的新引擎。在这个越来越注重健康的年代，独一酵素将成为风靡大陆地区的健康养生<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>宠儿<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>为什么说独一酵素将会成为未来持续畅销的养生圣品？不仅仅因为它采用的是台湾阿里山最为天然有机的果蔬原料，<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>年来坚持运用古法陶瓮酿制技术，让酵素更醇厚的同时，也避免原料经过机器高温加工而破坏酵素活性，是现代金属、玻璃器皿不能比拟的。此外，品质优良的酵素至少要经过<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>年以上的超长发酵期，独一酵素为了保证酵素的活性高，易于人体吸收，始终坚持质量源于天然的理念，用最自然无为的方式启动食物的能力并确保效果、来源的纯净。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span>　　放观整个生存环境，我国民众普遍存在酵素不足的问题，补充酵素，增强体质，已经成为我们应对文明病的重要选择。酵素几乎人人都需要，这是何其大的市场！<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>近年来，酵素产品异军突起，风靡全球，争相进入大陆市场，但大多品牌定位高端市场，价格轻奢，让普通消费者望而却步；而独一酵素秉承着企业对社会的回馈与关爱。产品定位填补了大陆市场的价格空白，实现<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>让每个人都能喝得起好酵素<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>的企业夙愿，其超高的性价比拥有强大的竞争力。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span>　　眼下，大陆酵素产业刚刚起步，未来将是酵素产业发展的黄金期。随着养生理念日益被重视以及营养观念不断的被推广，相信独一酵素就会卖得越来越好！<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br style=\"mso-special-character:line-break;\" /><br style=\"mso-special-character:line-break;\" /></p></span></span><br>符合南通独一生物科技有限公司代理商要求的客户可以直接留言与厂家联系。');
