INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('4369','玛卡（maca） 是由中国保健食品招商网会员发布的抗疲劳类招商信息：<br><P style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 14pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-themecolor: text1\" lang=EN-US>Maca</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-themecolor: text1\">（玛卡）</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">是一种植物，学名是</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Franklin Gothic Medium\',\'sans-serif\'\" lang=EN-US>Lepidium Meye Niiwaop</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">，原产于秘鲁中部基宁及帕斯科附近海拔<SPAN lang=EN-US>4000</SPAN>米以上的安第斯山和中国云南西北部海拔<SPAN lang=EN-US>3500</SPAN>米以上山区，色泽黄中带紫，类似萝卜，是高原唯一的十字花</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">植物。</SPAN></P>\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">由于现代生活的节奏加快，人们每天都要穿梭在各种场合，回到家里要应对家里的大大小小的事务，长期以往，人们的疲劳感会越来越严重，身体也会日渐衰弱，因免疫力下降而引起的各种各样的病症，这都是恶性循环的场景。我们期盼