INSERT INTO `destoon_sell_data_5` VALUES('4488','安可来福碱性生命液---安全又有效排酸 是由中国保健食品招商网会员发布的增强免疫力类招商信息：<br><p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">安可来福让他们不再受前列腺病痛折磨</span><span style=\"font-size:16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:32pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">常常有安可来福消费者向总部反馈：喝了安可来福碱性浓缩液之后，出乎意料地告别了慢性前列腺炎。黑龙江鸡西的张大爷这样描述：遇到变天就犯病，坐时间长了、受凉了也犯病，**疼、坐卧不安。老人因为痛风开始喝安可来福，没想到六、七年间痛风没再发作，前列腺炎也没再犯过。</span><span style=\"font-size:16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:32pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">前列腺炎是男性常见病和多发病，尿频、尿急、尿痛为主要症状，急性发作常会波及精索淋巴结、精囊、附睾等处。由于前列腺炎的发病机制未能完全弄清，使一些病例治疗缺少针对性，迁延难愈；前列腺处在较深的位置以及前列腺的脂质包膜阻碍药物到达，也造成前列腺炎反复发作难彻底治愈。长期病痛折磨使患者背上了沉重心理包袱，性欲减退、性功能低下、精神焦虑</span><span style=\"font-size:16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">……</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">慢性前列腺炎甚至会对周身产生影响，如变态反应性虹膜炎、关节炎、心内膜炎、肌炎等。</span><span style=\"font-size:16pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:32pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">科学家认为酸性废物聚积体内导致免疫力下降、器官功能减退。安可来福碱性浓缩液具有清除酸性废物改善器官功能、促进代谢增强免疫力以及消炎止痛功效，而且无毒副作用。安可来福经胃产生重碳酸钠再经肠道水孔直接进入血液循环，快速到达病灶发挥作用。痛风和前列腺炎都与酸性废物有关，所以喝安可来福碱性浓缩液收到良好效果是必然的。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:32pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">安可来福</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">Alkalife </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">碱性浓缩生命液，是美国安可来福国际有限公司的发明，是世界发明专利，由黄尚然（</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">Sang Whang</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">）先生发明，全球统一规格</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">37</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">毫升每瓶。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br /><br /></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">在中国（包括香港、澳门），安可来福的总公司是安可来福（大连）生物科技有限公司，作为安可来福专利的中国总部全权负责销售美国专利安可来福产品。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br /><br /></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">问：怎样辨别是否是正宗的安可来福呢？</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">答：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-si